  <name>Yum Extender</name>
  <summary>Graphical package manager</summary>
  <developer_name>Tim Lauridsen</developer_name>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">@APP_ID@.desktop</launchable>

  <description>
    <p>
      Yum Extender is a graphical package management application. It allows you to search and browse
      for packages to install,
      remove and update on your computer.
    </p>
    <p>It is designed to give you full control over the packages on your computer and to be used by
      all users.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse packages available for installation or update</li>
      <li>Browse packages installed on your computer</li>
      <li>Search packages by name, summary, description</li>
      <li>Browse Installed flatpaks</li>
      <li>Install, remove and update flatpaks</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

